data.description: Welcome home to this 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom split-level haven nestled in the heart of Hunters Crossing! Designed for seamless entertainment, this gem boasts a prime corner lot location, overlooking the tranquil community walking path and mere moments from the scenic New Windsor Reservoir. Revel in the convenience of an upper-level laundry room, ensuring utmost ease and efficiency. With added modern comforts including A/C, sprinkler system, and meticulously landscaped fencing, this home is better than new!
